<h2 id="section-top">General Surgery</h2>
</div>
<div class="col four-sm">
</div>
<div class="col three-sm" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_contentColumn1">
<div class="box">
<p class="module">
        This Department is managed by  
        <a href="/Services/Trusts/Overview/DefaultView.aspx?id=1431">Lewisham and Greenwich NHS Trust</a>
</p>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="service-locations clear">
<div class="panel edit-box">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<p class="address">General Surgery<br/>0208 333 3169</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div id="imageContent3ab1a5059d2146178d223428c1dcb258">
<div class="profile-pic">
<img alt="Theatre at LHT" border="0" id="ctl00_ctl00_ctl00_PlaceHolderMain_column1Content_column1Content_SummaryAndPhotoModule_PhotoView_DisplayImage" src="/Services/UserControls/UploadHandlers/MediaServerHandler.ashx?id=1852"/>
</div>
</div>
<p><strong>Welcome to the General and Vascular Surgery Department.  Below you will find basic information about the department, including a description of all of the clinics that we run.</strong></p>
<p>If you have any queries or issues you would like to discuss, please call us on 020 8333 3169.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>What services are available?</strong></p>
<p>We provide a range of general clinics including:</p>
<ul>
<li>2 week wait colorectal service </li>
<li>Colorectal service </li>
<li>Adult gallstone service </li>
<li>Adult hernia service </li>
<li>General Surgery </li>
</ul>
<p>Please note: Some general surgery conditions will be subject to approval under the exceptional circumstances policy.</p>
<p><strong> </strong></p>
<p><strong>Where are these services located?</strong></p>
<p>The General and Vascular Surgery Department operates from Suite 4, which is located on the 1<sup>st</sup> Floor of the brand new Kingfisher Building in the Pink Zone.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong>Further information</strong></p>
<p>For further information, including clinic times, referral details and key staff, please <strong><a href="http://www.lewisham.nhs.uk/our_services/surgery/general_surgery.aspx">visit the general and vascular surgery section of our website</a></strong>.</p></div>
</div>
</div>
